Create an Interactive To-Do List

Requirements:

Use HTML for the structure, CSS for styling, and JavaScript for interactivity.X
The to-do list should have the following features:
Add new tasks with a "Add" button.X
Mark tasks as complete with a "Done" button.X
Delete tasks with a "Delete" button.X
Filter tasks as "All," "Active," or "Completed."X
Clear completed tasks with a "Clear Completed" button.X
Use local storage to persist tasks even after the page is refreshed.X